From fe58796bd3cfbfc3d42e8a94207a957411db478b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claudio Bantaloukas <claudio.bantaloukas@arm.com>
Date: Thu, 8 Jan 2026 13:40:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] aarch64: Add tests checking use of arm_sve.h et al in a pch
 [PR123457]

These tests check that including files using aarch64 specific pragmas in
headers that become precompiled headers works.

Built and tested for aarch64-linux-gnu on top of Andrew's patch.

